**  for upgardtion is must required downtime but it take less time to upgarde ** that to application also should stop **
step-1:- check the version of mongodb 
    db.version()
    mongod --version
step-2:- before upgardation must take the backup of database
mongodump --out /path/to/....
step-3:- stop the service
systemctl status mongod | ps -ef | grep mongod
systemctl stop mongod 
step-4:- update the packages
yum update mongodb-org
step-5:- start the service 
systemctl start mongod 
step-6:- check the version
